Put him on as a fed or something.

41:05.212 --> 41:06.379
- Joe.
- Take care.

41:06.547 --> 41:08.882
Chief, always a pleasure.

41:09.049 --> 41:11.718
Hey, chief, good to see you again.
Hey, Tomas.

41:11.886 --> 41:13.636
See you, Papa.

41:14.889 --> 41:18.349
Okay, Danny, here, help me up.

41:18.976 --> 41:21.561
