41:36.869 --> 41:37.952
Okay?

41:40.372 --> 41:41.748
Danny.

41:43.959 --> 41:46.169
A man's gotta eat, no? Heh.

42:01.477 --> 42:05.939
Hey, Gonzales, wait up.
