55:30.410 --> 55:31.452
I'm sorry.

55:35.707 --> 55:38.000
I've always wondered, May...

55:39.085 --> 55:41.045
what was it like...

55:42.297 --> 55:44.590
after you watched your parents die.

55:44.758 --> 55:46.800
Did you go over to the bed?

55:47.761 --> 55:50.846
