55:51.222 --> 55:53.766
Did you try to shake them awake?

55:55.185 --> 55:56.602
How much blood?

55:56.770 --> 55:59.188
I'm just curious, was there...

56:00.357 --> 56:02.274
a lot of blood, May?

56:02.442 --> 56:04.443
Don't push me, Ned.

56:22.170 --> 56:25.964
- What the hell are you doing here?
- Take it easy, hotshot.

56:26.132 --> 56:27.758
I'm just checking up on you.

56:27.926 --> 56:30.636
I don't need you goddamn
babysitting for me, Trent.

56:31.596 --> 56:33.806
Why aren't you out
looking for who's hitting us?

56:33.973 --> 56:36.058
- That's great, Tomas.
- What's the first move?

56:36.226 --> 56:37.434
Door-to-door search?

56:37.644 --> 56:39.353
I'm sick of you.

56:40.647 --> 56:42.439
