- You are threatened.

58:15.742 --> 58:17.451
Tommy, Miguel, you in?
- I'm in, boss.

58:17.619 --> 58:19.161
- Me too.
Come on.

58:19.329 --> 58:21.121
Get it together.

58:21.289 --> 58:23.081
Five hundred.

58:33.426 --> 58:35.636
Okay, I'm out of here.

59:40.702 --> 59:42.035
Just a second.

59:45.540 --> 59:46.873
May Munro.

59:51.504 --> 59:53.422
Come on!

59:57.760 --> 01:00:00.345
