- Come on! Get up!

01:00:00.513 --> 01:00:03.265
Go in there! Get him!
Get the fuck in there!

01:00:04.851 --> 01:00:05.976
Get back.

01:00:07.353 --> 01:00:09.187
Keep them back.

01:00:11.983 --> 01:00:13.025
Come on, get them out!

01:00:13.359 --> 01:00:15.736
Get them out!

01:00:20.992 --> 01:00:22.784
